      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this beauty in person to believe it. It\u2019s in absolutely stunning condition\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it really shows in every little detail. If you're looking for that perfect, like-new ride without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve found it. I\u2019m so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have!",
