    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an uncompromising example of mechanical excellence, this vehicle features a meticulously maintained, naturally aspirated powerplant paired with a precision-weighted, short-throw manual gearbox. The drivetrain is anchored by a mechanical limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution during high-load cornering. The suspension geometry remains factory-spec, utilizing adaptive dampers and reinforced subframe bushings for surgical turn-in precision. Braking performance is anchored by ventilated rotors and four-piston monoblock calipers with zero thermal glazing. With a documented service history highlighting frequent fluid analysis and a pristine undercarriage free of oxidation, this car represents the pinnacle of its chassis code's performance envelope.",
