    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is, without hyperbole, the finest example of its kind currently on the market. Having been kept in a climate-controlled garage and meticulously maintained, the exterior boasts a deep, glass-like finish thanks to a professional-grade ceramic coating applied shortly after purchase. There are no rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings to be found; every panel is laser-straight. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state. The premium leather seats still retain their factory scent and firm bolstering, showing zero signs of wear or creasing. All technology interfaces, buttons, and switches function with crisp, tactile precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, reflecting a history of preventative maintenance performed exclusively by certified technicians. This vehicle drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line\u2014tight, responsive, and exceptionally smooth. For the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is your car.",
      "price": 48900.0,
