      "description": "We are proud to present an exemplary specimen of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in a state of unrivaled excellence, reflecting a history of meticulous stewardship and climate-controlled storage. From its flawless exterior finish to the pristine, untouched interior, every detail adheres to the highest standards of quality. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a vehicle in showroom condition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
