    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed manual transmission. Mechanically flawless, the double-VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with a structural foam and plate kit. The chassis remains rigid, supported by a factory-spec limited-slip differential and M-tuned suspension with fresh bushings. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the paint depth is consistent with factory tolerances, showing zero evidence of track use or inclement weather exposure. A true turn-key collector piece for the discerning purist.",
